74
00:03:28,830 --> 00:03:29,760
The images posted

75
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:30,920
on that so-called account

76
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,220
of Sheng Nina are fake.

77
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,960
Second, it's to confirm

78
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,940
if there's hacking.

79
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:37,550
I checked

80
