92
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:00,880
Right, right.

93
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:01,760
Well then.

94
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,340
I'll leave the rest to you.

95
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,220
Okay, bye-bye.

96
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,810
