118
00:04:50,910 --> 00:04:52,030
No one will say we bought

119
00:04:52,030 --> 00:04:53,780
the articles to clear our names.

120
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,220
Anyway,

121
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:57,000
we have to find a chance

122
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,220
to thank him in person.

123
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,620
Yang.

124
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:12,780
