125
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,540
I placed them on your desk.

126
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:16,260
Sure. Thanks.

127
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:18,300
These flowers are beautiful.

128
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:20,380
I'm the witness of your love.

129
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:21,700
Stop joking; stop it.

130
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:22,540
You get back to work.

131
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:51,580
(Tang Yang)

132
00:05:56,820 --> 00:05:57,980
(To make up for the past.)

133
00:05:57,980 --> 00:05:59,300
(From: Song Jing)
No, this...

134
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:01,900
("Tang Yang" recalled a message)

135
00:06:08,460 --> 00:06:10,980
("Tang Yang" recalled a message)

136
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:19,260
