137
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:21,500
He's usually busy.

138
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:23,580
He probably didn't see it.

139
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:27,180
(Jiang Shiyan)
What

140
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:28,500
