141
00:06:40,180 --> 00:06:41,020
Mr. Jiang.

142
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:41,940
Here's the thing.

143
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:44,580
I just sent you a picture of flowers.

144
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:46,580
When I saw them,

145
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:47,940
I thought they were from you,

146
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,100
