147
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,740
with them.

148
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,060
But I realized

149
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:53,620
they didn't seem to be from you.

150
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:56,260
So, who sent them?

151
00:06:56,780 --> 00:06:57,980
They're from Song Jing.

152
00:06:58,460 --> 00:06:59,540
