155
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:04,340
Does he want to leave here alive?

156
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:06,140
No, I don't know.

157
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:07,020
This person

158
00:07:07,020 --> 00:07:08,780
must have been crazy.

159
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:10,500
He must have lost his mind.

160
00:07:10,980 --> 00:07:12,300
Now, look.

161
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:13,740
Look at the flowers.

162
00:07:13,980 --> 00:07:15,980
I'll throw them in the trash can

163
00:07:18,260 --> 00:07:19,620
and let them sit

164
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:21,260
in this dark little corner,

165
00:07:21,260 --> 00:07:22,180
out of the sunlight.

166
00:07:22,180 --> 00:07:23,460
I won't water them.

167
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:24,580
I'll just let them

168
00:07:24,580 --> 00:07:25,940
wither and die here.

169
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,020
Is that okay?

170
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:28,140
If you think that's not okay,

171
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:29,660
I'll just beat them up a bit.

172
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:30,980
I'll beat them up.

173
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:31,820
Okay?

174
00:07:32,180 --> 00:07:33,100
Okay, okay, okay.

175
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:35,980
My Tang knows how to comfort me.

176
00:07:36,140 --> 00:07:36,980
Wait for me.

177
00:07:37,180 --> 00:07:38,420
I'll get you a bigger,

178
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:39,420
