179
00:07:39,580 --> 00:07:41,620
No, no, no, don't.

180
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:43,060
Please don't send it to the office.

181
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:44,180
That'd be too silly.

182
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:45,220
Many people are here.

183
00:07:45,220 --> 00:07:46,180
We can keep

184
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:47,940
our sweetness to ourselves.

185
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:49,100
I don't want

186
00:07:49,100 --> 00:07:50,300
