190
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:57,780
I'll remember it.

191
00:07:58,460 --> 00:07:59,580
So childish.

192
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:01,100
Take a picture of it?

193
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:02,180
Alright, got it.

194
00:08:02,580 --> 00:08:03,420
Bye-bye.

195
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:12,740
(Tang Yang)

196
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:13,900
Didn't you say it's childish?

197
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:15,260
(Jiang Shiyan)

198
00:08:15,260 --> 00:08:16,580
(Tang Yang)
Then I'll recall it.

199
00:08:18,980 --> 00:08:19,860
(Jiang Shiyan)
Saved.

200
00:08:28,340 --> 00:08:29,980
Come on, you've all worked hard.

201
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:30,940
Have some fruit.

202
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,260
I was looking for you.

203
00:08:33,380 --> 00:08:34,380
- Thanks.
- No problem.

204
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:35,300
