205
00:08:36,580 --> 00:08:38,180
Talk to Tang Yang.

206
00:08:38,380 --> 00:08:39,340
No idea what's wrong.

207
00:08:39,340 --> 00:08:40,460
She just got furious.

208
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:41,700
What's wrong?

209
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:44,460
Someone

210
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:45,780
