216
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:56,700
sent those flowers.

217
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:58,940
Or why would she throw away the flowers

218
00:08:58,940 --> 00:08:59,820
and stomp on them?

219
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:00,700
What a pity.

220
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:01,740
Yeah.

221
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:04,100
Please talk to her later.

222
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:06,500
Mr. Song, have some fruit.

223
00:09:08,180 --> 00:09:09,020
Okay.

224
00:09:10,820 --> 00:09:12,260
Don't you have plans tonight?

225
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:13,980
No.

226
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:16,020
I just

227
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:17,260
