229
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:19,780
with some gifts.

230
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:21,820
He has won

231
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:22,860
the Annual Economist Award

232
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:24,620
from Fortune Magazine.

233
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:25,700
I went to congratulate him.

234
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:27,740
He said he had a dinner party tonight,

235
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:28,620
so I left.

236
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:32,660
Song Jing told me

237
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:34,500
